com.northconcepts.datapipeline.diagnostic

Class Diagnostic

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.northconcepts.datapipeline.diagnostic.Diagnostic

  • public class Diagnostic
extends Object
    Helps diagnose environmental issues by collecting properties and sending them to https://northconcepts.com/contact.

    The properties collected are:

    • Name and email of sender if provided
    • Local date and timezone
    • Location of license file (if present)
    • Location of DataReader class file
    • Number of records transfered in a single job (out of 100 million records)
    • All JVM properties

    No local IP, machine, or geographic data are collected.

    Usage in code: new Diagnostic(email, firstName, lastName).send();

    Usage on command line: java -jar NorthConcepts-DataPipeline-4.1.0.jar com.northconcepts.datapipeline.diagnostic.Diagnostic "your-email@company.com" "your first name" "your last name"
